==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[response]]; something said or done in reaction to a statement or question.
#: ''Her '''answer''' to his proposal was a slap in the face''.
# A solution to a problem.
#:''The '''answer''' is...''
# Answer to an email. ([[reply]])

